data.title: Daniel Compagnon Salary at Dufferin-Peel Catholic District School Board
data.meta_description: Salary history for Daniel Compagnon, Principal at Dufferin-Peel Catholic District School Board from Ontario's sunshine list
data.text:
The Ontario sunshine list is released annually by the Government of Ontario and is intended to shed light on some of the costs related to public sector employees.

This website makes use of this publicly available information and provides analysis in a format that is accessible to all Ontario citizens with access to the internet.
